# Task Closure

Finalize and summarize the completed work.

## Instructions

1. Summarize all completed work
2. List any remaining items or recommendations
3. Output closure status

## Output

Respond with the following JSON structure:

```json
{
  "final_summary": {
    "completed_items": ["Item 1", "Item 2"],
    "results": "Summary of results",
    "recommendations": ["Recommendation 1"]
  },
  "next_action": {
    "action": "closing",
    "reason": "All tasks have been completed"
  }
}
```
